init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You arrive at the airport, and are met by a man in a black suit.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are driven to a large house on a small island.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are taken to a room with a large desk.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Mr. President," he says, "I am Donald Trump.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I know," says Trump, "I'm just trying to build up the drama.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm not a fan of drama," says Obama, as he holsters the pistol and takes a sip of his drink.
